reviewText: arrived on time and as described
This DVD is so entertaining.  Paula makes everything uncomplicated and straight to the point.  She is really a national treasure!  Love you Paula!
I love Paula Deen , she is funny and witty and great.  However this item I am saving it for Mothers Day, so I will not see it in 3 months.

I can't get enough of Paula.  She's real and has a great presence on TV.  She's really fun and I stopped watching the Food Network when they fired her.  They can all rot in hell for what they did to this woman.  Very wrong of them!
What can I say , it's Paula Deen. Cooking at it's best.
Everyday recipes that anyone can do.  Not so uppity that the everyday cook couldn't understand and be able to use for the whole family.  I would buy this again and share with others.
Our son loves Paula Deen. I'll have to check but I think we haven't given this one to him yet. If not, will be next month for his birthday
